description:
Towers are essential parts for building a castle. If your heroes are currently in need of a fortified dwelling, browse no further!

I made the towers with pretty much the same techniques as the walls: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0bBE0TV5aAA

Materials Used: XPS foam, PVA glue & acrylic paint

Music: https://www.bensound.com
title: Miniature Castle Tower for D&D / Wargaming
